title: OpenMSX-0.10.0-All_Machines_and_extensions-By CAWASAME.zip
description:
Hello everyone! I've been using the emulator openMSX (I'm using the 0.10.0 version now) for a long time and I've collected all existents ROMs of all machines and extensions. I completed all machines and extensions successfully!

I tested one by one and fix a lot of things, according to data contained in hardwareconfig.xml files (SHA1SUMS and names) in openMSX package. I worked very hard on it!

Now I wish to share with all of you.
